Paper: hep-th/9607227

Date: 1996-07-30

Title: Superbranes

Authors: P.S. Howe and E. Sezgin

Comments: 13p, latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B390 (1997) 133-142

A large class of supersymmetric extended objects is considered from theviewpoint of embeddings of super worldsurfaces into target superspaces. It isshown that a simple geometrical condition leads to the equations of motion forthe brane in many cases.